\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Problem Statement\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs56 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 As AI systems become more and more autonomous, they will encompass a larger and larger share of purchasing decisions. We\'92ve seen this play out in spaces that agentic AI is already highly prevalent ie software development and research with the rise of companies like supabase, vercel, and\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://fly.io/"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 fly.io}}\'a0in software and firecrawl, exa, and tavily in research. We expect this trend to continue and to spread to other verticals as agents are deployed in these verticals.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs52 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Functional Requirements\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs56 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 1) a fully deployed remote-MCP({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://developers.cloudflare.com/agents/model-context-protocol/"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 https://developers.cloudflare.com/agents/model-context-protocol/}}) server built on our public API methods({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://app.skyfi.com/platform-api/redoc"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 https://app.skyfi.com/platform-api/redoc}}) \
2) allows a user to conversationally place a SkyFi image order \
3) must confirm with user the price \
4) and require human confirmation before placing order \
5) must check feasibility and report this to the user before placing order \
6) allows a user to explore available data on skyfi through iterative search \
7) allows a user to conversationally explore their previous orders and fetch previously ordered images \
8) allows a user to conversationally explore feasibility of a task \
9) allows a user to conversationally explore different pricing options \
10) allows a user to conversationally set up aoi monitoring and notifications \
11) integrated with webhook so that an agent can conversationally inform the user when their aoi has new images (think an item in ChatGPT Pulse informing the user that there are new images available) \
12) authentication and payments support within the MCP \
13) ability to host the server locally \
14) stateless HTTP + SSE({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://blog.christianposta.com/ai/understanding-mcp-recent-change-around-http-sse/"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 https://blog.christianposta.com/ai/understanding-mcp-recent-change-around-http-sse/}}) \
15) allow for local use with credentials in stored JSON config \
16) AND cloud deployment with credentials sent in headers for multi-user access \
17) OpenStreetMaps integration \
18) and exposed tools comprehensive documentation on how to use the MCP with ADK({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://google.github.io/adk-docs/tools/mcp-tools/"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 https://google.github.io/adk-docs/tools/mcp-tools/}}), langchain({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://langchain-ai.github.io/langgraph/agents/mcp/"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 https://langchain-ai.github.io/langgraph/agents/mcp/}}), ai-sdk({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://ai-sdk.dev/cookbook/node/mcp-tools"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 https://ai-sdk.dev/cookbook/node/mcp-tools}}), Claude Web({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://support.anthropic.com/en/articles/11175166-getting-started-with-custom-integrations-using-remote-mcp"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 https://support.anthropic.com/en/articles/11175166-getting-started-with-custom-integrations-using-remote-mcp}}), and all the major provider APIs (openAI({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/tools-remote-mcp"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/tools-remote-mcp}}), anthropic({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/mcp"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/mcp}}), gemini({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/function-calling?example=meeting#mcp"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/function-calling?example=meeting#mcp}})) \
19) a demo agent using this MCP for geospatial supported deep research polished and ready to be opensourced\cb1 \
}